<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="F" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Furtherance" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Furtherance,</orth> a helping forward, assistance: <cit><quote>that may give f. to our expedition,</quote> <bibl n="shak. h5 1.2.301" default="NO" valid="yes">H5 I, 2, 301</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>entreat you to your wonted f.</quote> <bibl n="shak. 1h6 5.3.21" default="NO" valid="yes">H6A V, 3, 21</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>by your f.</quote> <bibl n="shak. per 2.1.160" default="NO" valid="yes">Per. II, 1, 160</bibl></cit>.
